{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"resume","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When a pack resumes after being suspended, it may begin by iterating over the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"already downloaded resources. As a result, the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" structure’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"countOfResourcesCompleted"},{"type":"text","text":" field may revert to 0 before rapidly returning to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the level of progress at the time the pack was suspended."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To temporarily suspend downloading, call the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-suspend"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Resumes downloading if the pack is inactive."}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/resume"]}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"resume"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(im)resume","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"resume"}],"title":"resume"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/resume","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/resume":{"title":"resume","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"resume","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/resume","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/resume","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"resume","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Resumes downloading if the pack is inactive."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePack","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","title":"MLNOfflinePack","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}]}}}